==English==
===Etymology===
From Greek φαντασμα phantasma (ghost) + αγορευειν agoreuein (to speak publicly)

===Adjective===
'''phantasmagoric'''

#Characterised by rapid changes in light intensity and colour.
#The quality of blurring real and imaginary elements as in a dream.

